# Structurizr generated artifacts — docs/architecture/workspace.dsl is the source of truth.
# The Mermaid exports (_export/*.mmd) ARE committed so the views render on GitHub without a
# Structurizr instance; refresh them whenever workspace.dsl changes (see the maintenance contract).
docs/architecture/.structurizr/
docs/architecture/workspace.json
docs/architecture/_export/*
!docs/architecture/_export/*.mmd
docs/architecture/build/
